 1995-04301995-03-140CAN PORTS,  TC,  ,  ,  ,  , 
PrecisAuthorization for the leasing by the VANCOUVER PORT CORPORATION to the CITY OF VANCOUVER, for a term of forty-nine (49) years, of some 2.5 hectares of waterfront land situated on Burrard Inlet, in the City of Vancouver, together with incidental licences, rights-of-way and future leasing rights, for the purposes of a public park (PORTSIDE PARK).
